# Backend API base URL for Codespace environments.
# Set this to your Codespace backend URL (the one ending in -3000.app.github.dev).
# Leave empty to use the Vite dev-server proxy (localhost:3000).
#
# Example:
# VITE_API_URL=https://your-codespace-name-3000.app.github.dev
# Leave blank — auto-detection in src/api/config.js handles Codespaces port-swapping.
